ise。不過，菊花識買唔識用，抵死。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以前 Lumia 個 OIS 係同 Zeiss 買埋，所以先咁高質。最有能力出 OIS 嘅 SONY 走去玩 EIS，其他廠又用普通 OIS，所以咪無一間追到。<br />\n<br />\n從來 Zeiss 只係負責鏡頭部分，佢唔會幫你搞埋 cmos 。不過，以當時 Nokia 同 Zeiss 嘅關係，可能有 team 人專門負責。<br />\n我就咁睇，以家 Leica 肯同菊花合作都係因為錢，冇以筆貼紙費 Leica 自己都好難捱，真正嘅合作只有 pan 記。Zeiss 反而以家仲係 lens 界第一，無咩必要走去賣logo，話唔定遲 d Nokia 出返部 1020 級數嘅機。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T05:01:43.000Z","msg":"條算法仲係微軟到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T05:15:39.000Z","msg":"係，所以咪冇得用 Pureview 個名，不過原理一樣，班底一樣，只係 cmos 唔同左，同埋要再用 monochrome denoise，所以成個算法要重寫。不過卑菊花班人搞到日拍全部 oversharpening，夜拍仲油過 xperia。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以，菊花係買人唔係買IP。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T07:58:05.000Z","msg":"如果專利只係一個名嘅話就好撚兒戲喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n論理一樣，但技術係唔一樣，屎為點買team人返去都好都唔可以用M$有嘅專利，所以佢要用類似嘅替代方案但效果就一定會唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以佢買成team人返去都係做唔到pureview一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外，其實唔好俾屎為呃到，佢話買pureview team，但其實幾個核心人物都無去到屎為，Juha Alakarhu去咗Axon、Tero Vuori去咗intel、Ari Partinen去咗apple，得Eero Salmelin去咗屎為，咁究竟成team嘅意思係點解呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有前Nokia imaging head，Damian Dinning仲出post屌屎為p20 pro唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/13/155631_d5fae34f0e93dd539a7d3c43d6740169.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F13%2F155631_d5fae34f0e93dd539a7d3c43d6740169.png&h=064ee531&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6dc3695b107c8c86cd0c9502f927ba9b259c306d","tid":659362,"uid":33653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20