\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n仲有前Nokia imaging head，Damian Dinning仲出post屌屎為p20 pro唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/13/155631_d5fae34f0e93dd539a7d3c43d6740169.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F13%2F155631_d5fae34f0e93dd539a7d3c43d6740169.png&h=064ee531&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n808 班友用左五年先攪左出黎, 但去到1020都證明唔到身價, 950XL 硬件反應同軟件都攪掂, 但微軟又決定收檔"}]}